<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-50 via-white to-green-50 rounded-3xl shadow-xl" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 mb-4">
      <div class="flex flex-col-reverse sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="bg-lime-500 text-white text-md sm:text-xl px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-lg font-bold">
          SINTASSI
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-lime-600">Il complemento oggetto</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-shrink-0 bg-red-600 text-white rounded-full w-10 h-10 sm:w-12 sm:h-12 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl">
        106
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>Il <strong>complemento oggetto</strong> è chiamato anche complemento diretto perché si collega al verbo direttamente, senza preposizioni;</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span>risponde alle domande: <strong>chi? / che cosa?</strong> → <em>Facciamo (che cosa?) una festa?</em> → <em>Invitiamo (chi?) gli amici!</em></span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-2xl border-4 border-yellow-300 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">1</span>
      <span class="bg-yellow-400 text-blue-900 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg font-bold mr-2">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      Dividi la frase in sintagmi, cerchia il predicato, sottolinea una volta il soggetto (se c'è) e due volte il complemento oggetto.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Eleonora ha disegnato un orso.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• D'estate il sole asciuga i panni.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Stasera porto del gelato alle fragole.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Prendi la tovaglia di cotone a quadri.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Filippo ha invitato Luigi alla festa.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-yellow-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <span class="text-gray-700">• Franca mandò dei fiori a sua madre.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-blue-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">2</span>
      Completa le frasi con un complemento oggetto adatto.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Samuele raccoglie</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input" placeholder=".......">
          <span class="text-gray-700">.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Guardiamo</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input" placeholder=".......">
          <span class="text-gray-700">.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Linda guida</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input" placeholder=".......">
          <span class="text-gray-700">.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-gray-700">• Quando porterai</span>
          <input type="text" class="border-b-2 border-blue-500 bg-transparent px-2 py-1 w-48" data-fill-blanks-target="input" placeholder=".......">
          <span class="text-gray-700">.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-green-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-green-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-green-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">3</span>
      Indica con X le frasi che contengono un complemento oggetto.
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex3_1" value="yes" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Ieri è venuto Pietro con un amico.</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex3_2" value="yes" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Può dirmi il prezzo della maglietta?</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex3_3" value="yes" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Questa strada attraversa gli Appennini.</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex3_4" value="yes" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Per cena ordinerei delle pizze.</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex3_5" value="yes" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Giovanni è stato qui?</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-green-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex3_6" value="yes" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">La statua fu scolpita da Michelangelo.</span>
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 4 -->
  <div class="mb-6 bg-white rounded-2xl border-4 border-purple-200 shadow-2xl p-4 md:p-6" data-controller="multiple-choice">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-purple-700 mb-4">
      <span class="bg-purple-600 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center mr-2">4</span>
      Qual è l'unica frase senza complemento oggetto?
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-purple-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex4" value="A" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Balliamo un tango sulle note di un vecchio disco.</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-purple-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex4" value="B" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Emily impara ogni giorno cose nuove.</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-purple-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex4" value="C" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Su un albero del giardino si è nascosto uno scoiattolo.</span>
      </label>

      <label class="flex items-start gap-2 bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-200 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-purple-100">
        <input type="checkbox" name="ex4" value="D" class="w-5 h-5 mt-0.5">
        <span class="text-gray-700">Chi vuole una fetta di torta al limone?</span>
      </label>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%= render partial: "shared/exercise_controls" %>

</div>
